values: so i was really tired today cause i was up till like four.  I woke up at like 1130 and had to go to baseball in fishkill.  We won our game 16-1, it was cold out.  We had another practice with my hardcore band yesterday, it was really fun.  Wow i am super tired, i am crying i am soo tired.  I have a super boring life and it sucks.  i am lonely and not really in a good mood.

well today was quite a good day.  All day was really really good for some reason.  Then I had band practice with my hardcore band Thenados.  This band is me, scott, dean, andrew glenn and we are getting another guitarist soon.  It was really fun though, we have four songs now and they are all sick.  Hopefully we are going to play at Ryan Lafaros party on this sat.  I am in a really good mood today, i wish that i could be in a mood like this every single day.

well i just started with live journal and i dont have too much to say.  I am starting to sell tickets for newborn tragedys may 14th show, so if anyone wants to go then you can ask me.  If u wanna hear us then go to www/purevolume.com/newborntragedy, then tell me if you like it or not.  This week is going to be long.
